hrough a working channel instead of trying to send to Telegram."},{"type":"text","text":"Both Telegram sessions timing out — delivery channel is down. I'll note this as the actual actionable issue:\n\n---\n\n🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | 20:34 UTC 14 Apr\n\nChanges detected:\n• ENDED: cron:ed2d0b5d (QLHV 5p Monitor) — finished normally, no issues\n• 🔴 TELEGRAM UNAVAILABLE: Both `telegram:group:-5163901258` and `telegram:direct:6053576134` are completely non-responsive (2+ consecutive gateway timeouts). Telegram delivery channel is down.\n\nPipeline: DEGRADED ⚠️\n• Active sessions: 3 (cron:6f3323ef ✅ cron:e7885813 ✅ telegram:group ✅)\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: Telegram gateway — delivery channel unresponsive. Bot may be disconnected or gateway overloaded.\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":180,"output":504,"totalTokens":44781,"cacheRead":43363,"cacheWrite":734,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776199122138,"responseId":"062dd8d3a99db64746cbdc51954df222","__openclaw":{"id":"329c7fee","seq":13}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: Agent Status to Lead","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776198729176,"sessionId":"788ab395-48cf-4c34-a7b2-2332f3bd3685","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":45769,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776198728659,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/788ab395-48cf-4c34-a7b2-2332f3bd3685.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive view of all active master-orchestrator sessions. Let me analyze